### 시설 수정 (UPDATE)
### PUT /facility/{facilityId}?adminId=1
### - facilityId는 실제 DB에 생성된 값으로 바꿔
### - status: AVAILABLE / UNAVAILABLE
### =========================
PUT http://localhost:8080/facility/1?adminId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "컴퓨터실 A-수정",
  "status": "AVAILABLE",
  "openTime": "10:00",
  "closeTime": "20:00",
  "location": "2층",
  "facilityType": "컴퓨터실"
}

